OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some patchy rain across the east.
OL,7,FThis afternoon will be mainly dry with
OL,8,Fjust a few showers. Some brightness
OL,9,Fbreaking through at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers slowly dying out
OL,12,Fthis evening. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud. A cold night with
OL,15,Fpatchy frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,18,Fwith some bright or sunny spells.
OL,19,FLight winds. Patchy rain in the
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
